pies creates list.\n    // MutationTestSummaryData adds to a Set.\n    // So duplicates will be ignored.\n    \n    // In original test: Mockito.mock(ClassInfo.class) created unique mocks?\n    // Yes.\n    \n    // So I need unique ClassNames.\n    Collection<ClassName> classes = new java.util.ArrayList<>();\n    for(int i=0; i<nrOfClasses; i++) {\n        classes.add(ClassName.fromString(\"class\" + i));\n    }\n    \n    final Collection<MutationResult> results = Collections\n        .nCopies(nrOfResults, makeResult());\n\n    return new MutationTestSummaryData(FILE_NAME, results, classes);\n  }\n\n}\n"}},"correlationId":"83afd7fd-c542-4065-904c-c3b3ae1d73ab"}
